		<title>TikTok遭法國調查推播內容 疑助長青少年心理問題</title>
		<link>https://firenews.com.tw/2025/11/05/tiktok%e9%81%ad%e6%b3%95%e5%9c%8b%e8%aa%bf%e6%9f%a5%e6%8e%a8%e6%92%ad%e5%85%a7%e5%ae%b9-%e7%96%91%e5%8a%a9%e9%95%b7%e9%9d%92%e5%b0%91%e5%b9%b4%e5%bf%83%e7%90%86%e5%95%8f%e9%a1%8c/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[火報 時事新聞]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Wed, 05 Nov 2025 07:09:01 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[時事]]></category>
